        "title": "docs: document auth profile failure policy contract",
        "body": "## Summary\n\n- Continue the inline-comment pass after PR #88554 on current `main`.\n- Document the auth-profile failure policy boundary that decides which failover reasons affect shared provider health.\n- Document heartbeat-only trigger policy prompt injection and the default non-heartbeat prompt shape.\n- Document embedded model fallback override precedence, including explicit empty override behavior.\n- Document RuntimePlan-first transcript policy resolution and legacy provider-runtime fallback adaptation.\n- Document embedded abort-settle cleanup timeout resolution and strict decimal env override behavior.\n- Document embedded attempt run decisions for write-lock timing, forwarded auth-profile provenance, unknown-tool guarding, hook gating, and tool-policy provider fallback.\n- Document the narrow replay-safe Codex app-server recovery retry gate for client-close and completion-idle failures.\n- Keep the change comment-only: no file header and no import-block comment.\n\n## Verification\n\nBehavior addressed: comment-only follow-up for auth-profile failover health policy, heartbeat trigger prompt policy, embedded model fallback override policy, attempt transcript policy selection, abort-settle timeout resolution, embedded run-decision contracts, and Codex app-server recovery retry policy; no runtime behavior intended.\nReal environment tested: local source checkout.\nExact steps or command run after this patch: git diff --check; git diff --check origin/main..HEAD; pnpm test src/agents/embedded-agent-runner/run/auth-profile-failure-policy.test.ts; pnpm test src/agents/embedded-agent-runner/run/trigger-policy.test.ts; pnpm test src/agents/embedded-agent-runner/run/fallbacks.test.ts; pnpm test src/agents/embedded-agent-runner/run/attempt.transcript-policy.test.ts; pnpm test src/agents/embedded-agent-runner/run/attempt.abort-settle-timeout.test.ts; pnpm test src/agents/embedded-agent-runner/run/attempt.run-decisions.test.ts; pnpm test src/agents/embedded-agent-runner/run.codex-app-server-recovery.test.ts.\nEvidence after fix: whitespace checks passed; focused Vitest shards passed with 6 auth-profile failure-policy tests, 7 trigger-policy tests, 3 fallback tests, 3 transcript-policy tests, 5 abort-settle-timeout tests, 9 run-decision tests, and 10 Codex app-server recovery tests.\nObserved result after fix: PR branch pushed from current main after confirming PR #88554 is merged into main.\nWhat was not tested: broader agent/gateway suites, because this PR only adds declaration documentation for tested helpers.\n",
